{"tid":2432622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【百思不得其解】其實點解仲有飛機從英國飛香港？","createTime":"2021-03-04T12:37:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T00:17:22.000Z","uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a6198e06b8fcc0f997198701e2abb868bc20b1e2","tid":2432622,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T12:37:38.000Z","msg":"由2020年12月25日凌晨零時起 ，所有於登機當天或之前21天曾逗留英國或南非超過兩小時的人士<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">將不會獲准登機前來香港</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁即係留學生，居英華人，甚至商家都唔上得機飛返香港，隔離21日都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁點解仲買到由英國飛香港既機票？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d527fd7062195f64b59ff8f797dc179f26a96ad0","tid":2432622,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T12:40:33.000Z","msg":"搭歐洲之星去法國上機<br />\n你知佢去過英國？"},{"pid":"9ca2a61c9c26723afbbe1e6232281d29c7c17fb0","tid":2432622,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"網上傳其實取消左好耐<br />\n有 negative result即可登機<br />\n但不知真假<br />\n係真既大家都唔想玩爛<br />\n其實英國確診數字已經回落左好耐<br />\n只要英國果邊比登機<br />\n就一定入到香港"},{"pid":"3ebb95bf5f0aa1a1fc774b05c8430601691e3f17","tid":2432622,"uid":208149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d527fd7062195f64b59ff8f797dc179f26a96ad0","tid":2432622,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T12:40:33.000Z","msg":"搭歐洲之星去法國上機<br />\n你知佢去過英國？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T13:09:27.000Z","msg":"Cta 有印<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1aebab57a6d4d1e5fa758c29f68aa17ff1154e","tid":2432622,"uid":38177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ebb95bf5f0aa1a1fc774b05c8430601691e3f17","tid":2432622,"uid":208149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d527fd7062195f64b59ff8f797dc179f26a96ad0","tid":2432622,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1